    "body" : "<p>you also can gather all properties on an annotation class </p>\n\n<pre><code>@JsonIgnoreProperties( { \"applications\" })\npublic MyClass ...\n\nString applications;\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 2836916,
      "reputation" : 21,
      "user_id" : 2437346,
